{"tid":651807,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【ATV又地震】傳行政總裁吳雨轉做顧問 亞視員工爆料講「死因」 6小時前97.1K 即時娛樂","createTime":"2018-05-03T11:23:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T11:52:33.000Z","uid":68367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f211f4ec0171238b02a595ec79ea06c02aedf4a9","tid":651807,"uid":68367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:23:07.000Z","msg":"ATV岀生啲舊垃圾 臭坑出臭草 爛泥扶唔上柄<br />\nSource<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180503&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=58146980\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180503%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D58146980&d=xEcxK8RUtCiVCfvhxqzm50zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=7cc2321e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180503%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D58146980&h=bb9a706e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180503&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=58146980</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【ATV又地震】傳行政總裁吳雨轉做顧問 亞視員工爆料講「死因」<br />\n6小時前97.1K<br />\n即時娛樂<br />\n亞洲電視於2016年4月「熄機」一年半，轉型OTT網絡電視「復活」唔夠半年，據《蘋果》了解，亞視近日「大地震」，亞視老闆唔再泵水，亞視CEO吳雨、營運總監區偉林嚟緊將轉做顧問，而製作總監林嘉穎舊年以私人理由遞信辭職，唔關今次「大地震」事。<br />\n<br />\n而據知亞視已經搵咗新管理層班子接手，但全部唔係行內人，同時今日亦有報道指，亞視業務發展未有起色，吳雨更已辭任行政總裁嘅消息。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">有亞視員工向《蘋果》透露，亞視今次搵咗大批無綫人過檔開台，同時請番唔少前亞視員工，佢哋對於無綫過嚟嗰班覺得係外邊人，唔太同無綫嗰班合作，更加有亞視舊員工話等亞視再遣散過，做嘢好唔積極，令到無綫過去做嘢嗰班工作上倍感困難。</span><br />\n<br />\n亞洲電視數碼廣播去年12月「借App還魂」，推出以手機Apps同OTT平台「無限復活」，今年1月29日先正式開台，當時行政總裁吳雨稱大老闆買咗王征嘅股份(新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2HLQxqU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HLQxqU&d=xEcxK8RUtCiVCfvhxqzm50zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=2202882a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2HLQxqU</a> )，吳雨指剛開台會拍一啲啱年青人睇嘅重頭劇，有啲同大陸合作嘅幾億投資大製作，佢話係一定要有大陸市場，加番啲香港元素，坦言一定要埋個大陸市場(新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2HLQVFS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HLQVFS&d=xEcxK8RUtCiVCfvhxqzm50zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=f28f52f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2HLQVFS</a> )，點知今日再次傳出「噩耗」。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/191939_5e8da9ae05a5c4d955031016a390a2ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F191939_5e8da9ae05a5c4d955031016a390a2ab.jpg&h=a889bd82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b4af13d8d8549ba7731c9b0c9e0698f91b37dad","tid":651807,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:33:19.000Z","msg":"仆街，亞視嚟嘅"},{"pid":"5012f63c96bf4922410bcae0aa3c7b64d07e567a","tid":651807,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:36:23.000Z","msg":"根本個名都臭到怨，班高層廢佬好似重未知乜事咁"},{"pid":"4ab86957263822b208df0412f86eb2057e5d2a85","tid":651807,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:50:53.000Z","msg":"亞視唔係早幾年執左啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecefe5a406b16b1eb164079086c7b77d45668bd2","tid":651807,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:52:15.000Z","msg":"吳雨唔是英皇架咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1192622bb521ddda636c8c8a1c6c51899ed2c4fb","tid":651807,"uid":15935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:52:33.000Z","msg":"咁撚有恆心同毅力，為乜啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}